{"id": "1518139831471833098", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "1510671767004385413", "author_name": "tofu_gutsu", "author_bot": false, "content": "質問失礼します。\n窮極の門、過ぎし日々の彼方2回、夢のような出会いの上級紀行のどれか1つだけ購入ならどれがおすすめでしょうか？所持札、覚醒体も載せておきます", "timestamp": "2026-06-21T06:25:41.497000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1518139830712668241", "filename": "925_20260621151746.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 794707, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1518139830712668241/925_20260621151746.png?ex=6a38d565&is=6a3783e5&hm=26a7d3c549e3dba6e4f7989a2655e721f98692441e2f481789398a56bb20ce63&"}, {"id": "1518139831128166480", "filename": "IMG_8756.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 185203, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1400058619726266462/1518139831128166480/IMG_8756.png?ex=6a38d565&is=6a3783e5&hm=2608ff5a67819e91eda0d4532a26155cef1c7fe1933f4cb7f36f38f99b01544b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1518147099508609134", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "724462977578958879", "author_name": "pei123", "author_bot": false, "content": "過ぎし日々はお得。目的の界域のキャラや札があるならオススメだけど運ゲー。\n夢のような上級は現状育てたいキャラがいないなら優先度低い。\n窮極の門はピックアップキャラや次の新覚醒体狙いとか、商店のシルバーコアで買える札欲しいならかなりお得。\nって感じでしょうか？", "timestamp": "2026-06-21T06:54:34.332000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1510671767004385413"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1518139831471833098", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1518148995510440097", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1510671767004385413", "author_name": "tofu_gutsu", "author_bot": false, "content": "ありがとうございます。もう一つ質問なのですがMorimensの方で実装済みのキャラが実装した時のためなら上級紀行と窮極の門、どちらの方がキャラを最終的に強くできそうですかね？それともサポーター的存在を狙って過ぎし日々の彼方を引いたほうがいいですかね？長文ですみません", "timestamp": "2026-06-21T07:02:06.374000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["724462977578958879"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1518147099508609134", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1518151288280449136", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "724462977578958879", "author_name": "pei123", "author_bot": false, "content": "強さでいうと覚醒体のレベルより素体の確保や3凸7凸の方が優先度高いので窮極の方でしょうか？\n上級紀行は覚醒体のレベル上げがメインの特典なので。コア集めてガチャの試行回数増やしたり商店の札完凸目指す方が良いんじゃないかなと思います！", "timestamp": "2026-06-21T07:11:13.013000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1510671767004385413"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1518148995510440097", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1518151827445514300", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "724462977578958879", "author_name": "pei123", "author_bot": false, "content": "過ぎし日々は狙いのキャラがいるなら運ゲーしてみてもいいとは思います！自己責任で笑", "timestamp": "2026-06-21T07:13:21.560000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
